Do they decide before or on 1 June 2020? If they say by 1 June, I assume they won't do it on the 31 May or before but there remains considerable uncertainty around this. Maybe they feel forced to announce their decision earlier if other governments increase their pressure on them. Let's see what happens in the coming days. [1] https://www.gjopen.com/comments/comments/1036917
