@sebawi Reducing the probability of the "Yes, before 1 June 2020" option. I'm switching my P's between May and June since the pressure for clarification coming from many countries is high and should press Saudis to decide. [1] If they decide this month cancellation or suspension seems more likely. [2] If nothing happens till the end of May I'll come back to my previous P's 0-70-0-30 and increase P("No") by about 15% every week. For reasoning, you can read the arguments under my previous forecast.
